  <summary>2/24/2015--Introduced.
Medicare Access to Rehabilitation Services Act of 2015

This bill amends title XVIII (Medicare) of the Social Security Act to repeal the existing caps on physical therapy, occupational therapy, and speech-language pathology services.</summary>
